    "subtype": "siege_weapon",
    "text": "Another design originating from the snow-covered land of Irrisen, the volley gun trades the power of black-powder cannons for a high rate of fire at a much smaller caliber. The nine barrels of the volley gun are triggered via a crank, rotating around the central shaft. The weapon is reloaded by slotting a single block placed into the breach, allowing each of the nine barrels to be fired before this mounted gun needs to be reloaded.",
